    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:border-gray-800 dark:text-gray-400">
      <p>AI-Me Discovery Manifest Specification v0.1 — Spec: CC-BY 4.0 · Code: Apache-2.0</p>
